"```sql\nSELECT \n  (COUNT(CASE WHEN c.hasContentWarning = 0 THEN 1 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*)) AS percentage_without_content_warning\nFROM \n  cards c\nJOIN \n  legalities l ON c.uuid = l.uuid\nWHERE \n  l.format = 'commander' AND l.status = 'legal';\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the percentage of cards that are legal in the \"commander\" format and do not have a content warning. It uses a `JOIN` to connect the `cards` and `legalities` tables based on the `uuid` column, and applies the conditions specified in the question."